{"id": 2867, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x兰蔻防晒霜】现如今你还会为哪些“XXX就不会老”的真理买单？", "description": "事实证明，“Anti-Social”和“Anti-紫外线”之间，总有一件事是对的。", "record_count": 12188, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190326152306UnpQmzoXHlAC9tbY.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-27T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 335872, "content": "不要熬夜！\n不要熬夜！\n不要熬夜！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1160, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378846}, {"id": 335873, "content": "躲在家里", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620498}, {"id": 335874, "content": "好好涂防晒 早睡觉不熬夜 少吃糖多喝水", "image": null, "praise_count": 253, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565107}, {"id": 336130, "content": "我记得之前有个话题说\n中国人的审美时候\n小女孩和老女人这两档\n没有mature这一档\n\n可是明明成熟也很有魅力", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434017}, {"id": 336133, "content": "多看看艺术展\n别老想着拍照", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433882}, {"id": 336134, "content": "不要用一边牙齿咀嚼，不要总靠着一边睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433929}, {"id": 336139, "content": "老不是重点，重点是不防晒容易得皮肤癌\n欧美小麦色肌肤流行，其实很伤啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433996}, {"id": 335884, "content": "大发快三回血技巧导师Q641405077", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620595}, {"id": 336140, "content": "不觉得自己老就不会老", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433847}, {"id": 336142, "content": "在做好日常护理的前提下接受慢慢变老的现实 毕竟大自然的规律谁也没法抵抗（摊手手", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434056}, {"id": 336145, "content": "饮食健康", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433995}, {"id": 336146, "content": "Anti-Social 可怕，Anti-紫外线 有用", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434023}, {"id": 335893, "content": "自信的人很年轻", "image": null, "praise_count": 99, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162821}, {"id": 335894, "content": "保持年轻的心态就不会老", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620652}, {"id": 335895, "content": "早睡运动", "image": null, "praise_count": 90, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615113}, {"id": 335900, "content": "接受并爱自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620672}, {"id": 335912, "content": "自己做自己的心理咨询师", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620677}, {"id": 335918, "content": "开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1617827}, {"id": 335923, "content": "防晒 抗糖 早睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 182, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1582723}, {"id": 335924, "content": "多防晒，斑就少", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620734}, {"id": 335925, "content": "爱运动不会差", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1600513}, {"id": 335926, "content": "开心就不会老", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1612721}, {"id": 335928, "content": "一针回到六年前", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181495}, {"id": 335930, "content": "好奇为什么会有这样的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620792}, {"id": 336447, "content": "从前一直嫌涂防晒霜麻烦，但突然有一天身边出现一个皮肤癌。我的天，这才意识到防晒的重要性", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424920}, {"id": 335937, "content": "爱笑的女生眼纹不会太少", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620843}, {"id": 335940, "content": "我想说有次误打误撞的买了这个防晒真的好好用！！！很真诚", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 969118}, {"id": 335941, "content": "防晒啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143922}, {"id": 336454, "content": "不会啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555110}, {"id": 336458, "content": "我可以老，但我不能放弃我喜欢的事情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195214}, {"id": 335947, "content": "枸杞泡起来 胳膊腿儿动起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620240}, {"id": 335948, "content": "多睡觉吧，最近我每天睡八九个小时，很多时候脸都忘了洗，没做面膜，皮肤还是比之前好了很多", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1608380}, {"id": 335951, "content": "多养生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620959}, {"id": 335952, "content": "少看手机📱，远离地心引力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496175}, {"id": 336976, "content": "防晒 戒糖 喝水 运动 早睡 护肤 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1625819}, {"id": 335956, "content": "15岁的我笑了笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557940}, {"id": 335701, "content": "打开运动细胞，精神状态和体力都会好很多", "image": null, "praise_count": 1351, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 335957, "content": "xxx不会老？？哈哈哈我想多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433994}, {"id": 335702, "content": "抗糖化难道不是衰老的第一要务吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 327, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 335958, "content": "女人是水做的，多喝水不会老呀，又不用花钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433941}, {"id": 335703, "content": "俗话说“养儿不防老，防晒才防老”", "image": null, "praise_count": 565, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 335959, "content": "早睡早起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433966}, {"id": 335704, "content": "保持好奇心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1439, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 335960, "content": "多 运 动", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124700}, {"id": 335705, "content": "爱笑的女孩运气都不会太差，爱防晒的女孩都比较不会老", "image": null, "praise_count": 1972, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 335961, "content": "让自己开心才不会变老", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433975}, {"id": 335706, "content": "少看电视多看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 717, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 335962, "content": "防晒啊！抗紫外线真的很重要！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433964}, {"id": 335963, "content": "少喝酒，多喝奶", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433902}, {"id": 335964, "content": "运动起来，健身吧少女！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433955}]}